text: Teofil Józef Wilski (October 16, 1935 - March 26, 2022) was a Polish Roman Catholic prelate. He was auxiliary bishop of Kalisz from 1995 to 2011. Wilski was born in Skubarczewo, Poland. He became a priest in 1960. Wilski died on March 26, 2022 in Ostrów Wielkopolski, Poland at the age of 86.Bishop Teofil Józef Wilski † ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Polish Roman Catholic bishops
